{"tid":1467181,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[考古] 梁天琦致香港人的信：懇請不要被仇恨支配自己","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T02:13:30.000Z","uid":53666,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a591f08d767cfc61c0489ae63128bea40acbda55","tid":1467181,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:28.000Z","msg":"請大家重讀一次烈士遺命:<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/D-Rc2-RU8AEyogM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FD-Rc2-RU8AEyogM.jpg&h=79409fc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">... 抗爭時間久了 ... 一定要堅持下去。 </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n已經有人提示, 就算出坦克車, 64 重演, 中共撕破面皮反檯,<br />\n<br />\n全世界都只係會口頭譴責。 出兵打大陸? 無可能。<br />\n制裁? maybe. <br />\n但香港會被一國一制。<br />\n<br />\n但係對於攬炒派嚟講, 呢個先係最佳結局。<br />\n既然係咁, 試下由呢個角度出發推演:<br />\n<br />\n出坦克嘅原因得一個, 就係運動<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">持續</span></span></strong></span>到一個地步, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">動搖共產黨政權。</span></span></strong><br />\n一日你班暴徒做唔到呢點, 佢都只係當你幫佢R痕。<br />\n<br />\n你班友今日阻旅客、用私刑, 林鄭真係會忍唔住笑出嚟。<br />\n因為再咁落去, 成個運動一定散!!! 係自己散!<br />\n<br />\n所以請唔該, 大家用最清醒嘅意志, 提醒自己點樣做好每一步。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WE SHALL NEVER SURRENDER!</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.pinimg.com/originals/fd/7b/fb/fd7bfb848297c0200a542b1f5e4ac015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.pinimg.com%2Foriginals%2Ffd%2F7b%2Ffb%2Ffd7bfb848297c0200a542b1f5e4ac015.jpg&h=8b4ef87d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d56e0e0704ccdbfe29421068e2c644caba480491","tid":1467181,"uid":53666,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:08:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">梁天琦致香港人的信：<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">懇請不要被仇恨支配自己</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦致香港人的信/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%A1%2F&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3Ijwu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=955b8662\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E8%87%B4%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E4%BF%A1%2F&h=44c9502c\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦致香港人的信/</a>"},{"pid":"a438f7d23befc5ef8fc41e76a5816e47ef1906fc","tid":1467181,"uid":53666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"推。<br />\n<br />\n電光火石間, 點樣做先最啱?  <br />\n沒有完美答案, 但永遠請理智行先!!!!"},{"pid":"e465ff25fbaf3502f01dbe2fd8cc6e5c2edbd684","tid":1467181,"uid":126309,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"有巴打講過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">連儂牆就撕一貼百<br />\n對家內鬼就捉一滲百</span><br />\n捉鬼只會沒完沒了，仲會弱我軍心<br />\n大家只需提醒同路人提防就夠<br />\n<br />\n返回最初0805、0811發現有鬼果句<br />\n<strong>小隊行動，小心行事</strong><br />\n<br />\n請再套用天琦果句"},{"pid":"af539f38129321e6bcc525e81bc2f82a2ba96558","tid":1467181,"uid":302679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:05.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ea467792e837bde134acd3b7dc3c68d93a9d7070","tid":1467181,"uid":302679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:39.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8673a8dfa553c3f60bdbf52df7de39839493e30c","tid":1467181,"uid":302679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5ef18526230d7db9f0aab6b35ff510d12da2cc57","tid":1467181,"uid":53666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:53.000Z","msg":"另外想推一下呢個POST:<br />\n【反送中】專業Gamer 同你分析機場集會，